<p class="lead border-top border-1 pt-2">
  At 3E PCB Software, we are dedicated to delivering cutting-edge Engineering Automation software, solutions, and
  services tailored for the printed circuit board (PCB) industry. Our commitment is to provide optimal solutions that
  address the intricate and demanding challenges of modern engineering requirements, fostering key customer partnerships
  along the way.
</p>
<p class="lead border-bottom border-1 pb-2">
  Our innovative solutions become the cornerstone for PCB design and manufacturing processes, enabling our partners to
  achieve unprecedented efficiency and quality. Our goal is to be the driving force behind the evolution of the PCB
  industry, pushing the boundaries of what's possible in engineering automation.
</p>
<p>
  With a rich heritage spanning almost four decades in PCB manufacturing and over a quarter-century in software
  development, the 3E PCB Software team stands on a foundation of deep industry knowledge and technical expertise. The
  beginning of Engenix in 1998 marked our response to the market's call for an independent engineering automation
  solution, and since then, we have been at the forefront of innovation in the PCB software domain.
</p>
<p>
  Our strategic partnership with Aptean underscores our dedication to delivering unparalleled value and service
  excellence and provides stability and security four our clients.
</p>
<p>
  Recognized as an indispensable asset by leading PCB manufacturers across the globe, Engenix® continues to provide
  mission-critical functionality with indispensable automation.
</p>
